ratioOptionalMavenDependenciesTimeLine.description: This metric shows the ratio of optional dependencies over the total number of dependencies.
ratioOptionalMavenDependenciesTimeLine.name: Ratio of optional Maven dependencies

ratioUnusedOSGiImportedPackages.description: This metric shows the ratio of OSGi Import-Package that are not actually used in the code.
ratioUnusedOSGiImportedPackages.name: Ratio of unused OSGi Import-Package

spreadOfErrorPronenessTimeLine.description: This metric shows the spread over the project's files of style violations which make the code error prone, over time.
spreadOfErrorPronenessTimeLine.name: Spread of error prone files over the system

spreadOfInefficienciesTimeLine.description: This metric shows the spread over the project's files of style violations which indicate inefficiencies, over time.
spreadOfInefficienciesTimeLine.name: Spread of files with inefficiencies over the system

spreadOfStyleViolationsTimeLine.description: This metric shows the spread of style violations over the project's files, over time.
spreadOfStyleViolationsTimeLine.name: Spread of files violating the coding standards over the system

spreadOfUnderstandabilityIssuesTimeLine.description: This metric shows the spread over the project's files of style violations which indicate understandability issues, over time.
spreadOfUnderstandabilityIssuesTimeLine.name: Spread of files with understandability issues over the system

testCoverageHistoric.description: This metric shows the history of the Java unit test coverage, estimated statically.
testCoverageHistoric.name: Unit test coverage (all methods)

testCoveragePublicHistoric.description: This metric shows the percentage of public Java methods covered by unit tests, over time.
testCoveragePublicHistoric.name: Unit test coverage (public methods)
